[
  {
    "startTime": 3.37,
    "endTime": 4.871,
    "text": "Spearfishing in Hawaii."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.938,
    "endTime": 7.874,
    "text": "I'm like a fish out of water."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.941,
    "endTime": 11.443,
    "text": "Thank god, I've got free diving champ Kimi for a guide."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.511,
    "endTime": 12.911,
    "text": "She makes it look so easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.384,
    "endTime": 18.852,
    "text": "Damn, she's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.755,
    "endTime": 24.823,
    "text": "Despite my fetching camouflage, I can't hit a thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.85,
    "endTime": 28.862000000000002,
    "text": "You were that close!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.763,
    "endTime": 30.630000000000003,
    "text": "That close."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.697,
    "endTime": 31.730999999999998,
    "text": "Don't get frustrated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.82,
    "endTime": 32.866,
    "text": "Oh, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.932,
    "endTime": 34.833000000000006,
    "text": "Like, really. You were almost there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.901,
    "endTime": 36.42,
    "text": "That was a good fish, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.54,
    "endTime": 40.339999999999996,
    "text": "How do you keep your breath under such control?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.407,
    "endTime": 43.242,
    "text": "Because you're holding on to the seabed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.309,
    "endTime": 45.144,
    "text": "You have the spear in the other."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.211,
    "endTime": 49.65,
    "text": "And the current is pushing you back and forth the entire time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.71,
    "endTime": 49.97,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.12,
    "endTime": 52.018,
    "text": "It's a lot of work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.085,
    "endTime": 53.253,
    "text": "Right. Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.319,
    "endTime": 54.621,
    "text": "That was awesome, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.43,
    "endTime": 66.833,
    "text": "Right, hold my breath."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.9,
    "endTime": 70.13600000000001,
    "text": "Line up my sights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.203,
    "endTime": 72.42,
    "text": "This is just like shooting fish in a barrel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.72,
    "endTime": 76.509,
    "text": "A very big Pacific-Ocean-sized barrel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.576,
    "endTime": 77.309,
    "text": "Bingo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.987,
    "endTime": 90.49,
    "text": "Whoo, whoo, whoo, whoo!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.557,
    "endTime": 91.624,
    "text": "Awesome!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.691,
    "endTime": 92.82600000000001,
    "text": "A beauty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.892,
    "endTime": 97.063,
    "text": "I held onto the rock, bent down the corner and just waited for him to pop up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.13,
    "endTime": 98.698,
    "text": "Oh, that was awesome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.765,
    "endTime": 99.466,
    "text": "Whoo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.532,
    "endTime": 100.887,
    "text": "I don't want to come out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.12,
    "endTime": 102.068,
    "text": "- I know. - Amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.5,
    "endTime": 103.67,
    "text": "Honestly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.736,
    "endTime": 104.70400000000001,
    "text": "What a teacher."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.771,
    "endTime": 106.74,
    "text": "It makes you want to live under water."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.85,
    "endTime": 107.874,
    "text": "It's that exciting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.941,
    "endTime": 109.108,
    "text": "You don't want to come up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.175,
    "endTime": 110.31,
    "text": "I want to go back again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.476,
    "endTime": 112.17999999999999,
    "text": "This is an enenui."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.23,
    "endTime": 113.28,
    "text": "- An enenui? - Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.36,
    "endTime": 115.081,
    "text": "And did you grow up eating fish like this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.148,
    "endTime": 119.92,
    "text": "- My dad would go spear fishing to put food on the table, and this is one of the main fish that he fed us. - Wow, cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.12,
    "endTime": 121.354,
    "text": "How cool. Beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.421,
    "endTime": 122.89,
    "text": "So you literally eat this raw?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.955,
    "endTime": 124.91,
    "text": "We always would eat this fish raw."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.12,
    "endTime": 132.165,
    "text": "This fish eats a lot of seaweed, and so it tastes different all on different parts of the island depending on what type of seaweed is growing there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.232,
    "endTime": 133.333,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.399,
    "endTime": 134.367,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.434,
    "endTime": 135.902,
    "text": "Can you taste that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.969,
    "endTime": 137.269,
    "text": "That's delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.337,
    "endTime": 138.95,
    "text": "And it does taste a little bit seaweedy, a little bit salty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.2,
    "endTime": 140.90699999999998,
    "text": "A lot of times we add seaweed for flavor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.74,
    "endTime": 141.98000000000002,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.02,
    "endTime": 143.98000000000002,
    "text": "With this fish, it's already pre-seasoned."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.08,
    "endTime": 144.644,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.711,
    "endTime": 145.61200000000002,
    "text": "Because of its diet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.747,
    "endTime": 152.71900000000002,
    "text": "I mean, it was like the perfect trip to any fishmonger you'll ever go to your entire life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.785,
    "endTime": 159.59199999999998,
    "text": "I didn't think it would taste that good, and my god, without any dressing, without any chili or any soy, and so that's got me thinking now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.659,
    "endTime": 166.85,
    "text": "You know, do I make this feast predominantly around the fish locally, or is it meat right now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.97,
    "endTime": 168.668,
    "text": "Honestly, I'm spoiled for choice."
  }
]